### 8. Department Workspace

Department Workspace คือพื้นที่รวมของแต่ละแผนก

Common department modules:

```text
Department Workspace
├── Dashboard
├── Documents
├── Files
├── Notes
├── Work Memory
├── Activity Timeline
├── AI Assistant Panel
├── Pending Reviews
├── Approvals
